---
/* Final CTA section - The bridge between the story and the action */
---

<section class="w-full py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-theme-base relative overflow-hidden transition-colors duration-500">
  
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] border border-brand-gold/5 rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
    
    

    <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl text-theme mb-8 leading-tight">
      Help Us Rebuild a Small Space <br /> 
      <span class="italic text-brand-gold">for a Living Craft</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="font-sans text-theme-muted text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      With a stable workspace, this craft can continue to exist, and slowly be shared with others who may benefit from learning it.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6">
      
      <a href="/support" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-brand-gold text-theme-contrast font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:brightness-105 transition-colors duration-300 rounded-sm">
        Support This Project
      </a>

      <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/yourlink" target="_blank" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 border border-theme text-theme font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-theme-surface transition-colors duration-300 rounded-sm">
        Buy Me a Coffee
      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <a href="/proposal.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-theme-muted hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
        </svg>
        Download Full Proposal (PDF)
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>